<title>USA: Medicus Systems FY 1997 shr rises.</title>
<headline>Medicus Systems FY 1997 shr rises.</headline>
<dateline>EVANSTON, Ill. 1997-07-29</dateline>
<text>
<p>MEDICUS SYSTEMS CORP.</p>
<p>			 (In thousands, except per share data)</p>
<p>							Fiscal Year Ended</p>
<p>						  May 31,	   May 31,</p>
<p>						     1997	     1996</p>
<p> REVENUES					 18,270	   19,794</p>
<p>   Restructuring charges		     2,800	    4,662</p>
<p>   Stock repurchase			    1,690		  -</p>
<p> OPERATING LOSS				 (7,355)	  (7,445)</p>
<p>  Interest and other income		    367		556</p>
<p> LOSS FROM CONTINUING OPERATIONS	  (4,419)	  (4,073)</p>
